            Publish your OOS to <a href="/" class="text-otp-300 hover:text-otp-200 underline">orgtp.com</a> so other organizations can browse it, compare against it, and learn from your patterns. You read theirs the same way. This is where the transactive memory effect kicks in.
          </p>
